    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, dependable ride without breaking the bank? This car could be exactly what you need! It's in fair condition \u2014 it starts up reliably and gets you where you need to go day after day. You'll notice some signs of age and normal wear, both inside and out, but nothing that gets in the way of everyday driving. If you're after a practical, no-fuss vehicle at a reasonable price, this one deserves a serious look!",
