    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Affordable & Functional \u2014 A Solid Fair-Condition Find! \u2014 Looking for a reliable ride without the premium price tag? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and gets you where you need to go, but does show its age with some visible wear and minor issues you'll want to address over time. It's not perfect, but it's honest, and at this price point it offers real value for a budget-conscious buyer who wants a dependable daily driver. Come take a look \u2014 what you see is what you get, and that's a promise!",
      "price": 19500.0,
